name: Tensor
reason: The dominant professional NFT trading platform on Solana. High utility but significant venture capital backing and insider allocation necessitates a moderate score.

name: Magic Eden
reason: The leading cross-chain NFT marketplace with deep roots in Solana. Robust revenue model and infrastructure status, balanced by institutional ownership.

name: Metaplex
reason: The underlying protocol standard for nearly all NFTs on Solana. Crucial ecosystem infrastructure with a DAO structure, though early supply was tightly held.

name: Hadeswap
reason: An automated market maker for NFTs allowing instant liquidity. Innovative model but lower market cap and higher volatility compared to order-book marketplaces.

name: Dust Protocol
reason: Utility token for the DeGods and y00ts ecosystem. Value is derived heavily from social sentiment and ecosystem bridging, leading to price volatility.

name: Blocksmith Labs Forge
reason: Token powering a suite of NFT tools and launchpad services. Community-centric distribution with a focus on utility for holders.

name: Rain.fi
reason: Lending and borrowing protocol using NFTs as collateral. Generates real yield through interest, positioning it as a productive asset within NFT-Fi.

name: Gari Network
reason: Social token for a short-video app. High insider score due to corporate backing and centralized platform control, with complex tokenomics.
